item.title: [HIVE-19990] Query with interval literal in join condition fails
item.description:
Reproducer

> create table date_dim_d1(
	d_week_seq                int,
	d_date                    string);

> SELECT 
       d1.d_week_seq
FROM   
       date_dim_d1 d1 
       JOIN date_dim_d1 d3 
WHERE  
       Cast(d3.d_date AS date) > Cast(d1.d_date AS date) + INTERVAL '5' day ;

Exception

org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.parse.SemanticException: '5 00:00:00.000000000' encountered with 0 children
